[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering Java reflection access**\n\nI'm thinking about whether to use ModuleMemberAccessor behavior instead of ReflectionMemberAccessor. ReflectionMemberAccessor can access private fields, but I wonder about the differences in module access. Is it possible to access private fields or methods in JDK classes using the public API? With Java 17, ReflectionMemberAccessor throws an InaccessibleObjectException when trying to set accessibility for private fields in java.lang. Maybe I should consider using InstrumentationMemberAccessor for module opening instead.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0ede01fd727da590016a21aa3d39148193b3cf9b7a2c39a19c\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqIaplJJkcllXB-TFNczznImt12ApMPrDyMCmOWnAqLx2vrcBIMV5ZcSGUSDQYG2ipqv2ggCq_WoIBk9IOeZ80xFA2rvlCVYeEmBPWZeob4ET1wWCkH9EKIsIlhLGYI5onB-d9Gz0471x-hzit_y5RL5LkRcfDJ5VdF9T8l5pW40QyW0zzeYzkaw5PK-C0jobx-Pj6sIap4hBKke5S3ZEHnjomGYoucJG9c_ZCsveAikej7vZ2e1QGaW0X4hw8Uo659ePdR8g_J-BpNO6bIYAMmXPZ4YgQ7ygxm8mQ82DOB5_yI1f33gzDrGyR3rgL3-z7QMhyxi9VnZQf8VBadCm8zPf2_-tT1W7296uwHemPB9xB-XFu-RuS5z6i7a2P2ozKQlijQalu17tuRJs8tUyDSfpMnFyQ8Y_27oaokGS6Jr_uaf5a7IHGr6xSEFSvwfH3ikdFZBjuFXa_4poFzDkeu1WaP7QhwEI7Pjp7ugBCbCA9XE7u51R2kUBg1Ns-sn5VE4ek_bAL3BlRs8zzd9iH2t2y6AJlSckj-Vktk3oj5RR8h7NggQWH2IsQBzNJAzViRo9WLU5rYVk7vOMUQEMeYcE3S_LS9q_XdKrBXLpQNYFZ6rjdVL7zWyTy9e4FvRBi7EqrfygIpPuRpN-0WELf7Yrd17ljUozmgccXUUAYnY1Jl5zS_XHFXle_drYwQpVi99B7XXxNRAPXD1yUXVunOf_UUqEm_56HY-4og-wBwwxSoOG-Mt0uz-O7Uxh-oPyhjgPfEP9_VNE2TU8lVmIw_uSP2RNeowmjS7oITTKuUvsKRVa1FVKogyAfaCSV_PR92qjb21rcoMg7vIL002yJbQByu7Iuqu_-JqmHIiS67Ganls_0n-JhlK4mdOynCNDU7YxNHBz0GGuqjJzhLMZESEAMJev3e2fRaReomqjbMIzEfTZw1kr1M_CUbPRGn3LvqbF4TqQ9x2oN353NarvOAc-XAdr1xtBObiWYbpzdOdUiEsBhMiodtcs22sMqqhnDcveMEavaKxE4m-EYtc0eUqxDkqLnSMa_wggs7BNKmRLUxj2YVDmiUVDT5w_gNAAreWmD3GjmnghxcwO-g6ipwzs8IpjwTT9RywLWZ6ylByBFhvrrzB6XQwbrlXt06a2TBnrySkClk3jp7V